#include<stdio.h>
int main(){
    long long unsigned int a, b, count, f1, f2, temp;
    while(scanf("%llu %llu", &a, &b)){
       if(!a && !b) break;
       count=0;
       f1=1, f2=2;
       while (1) {
          if(f1>b) break;
          if(f1>=a) count++;
          temp=f1;
          f1=f2;
          f2+=temp;
       }
       printf("%llu\n",count);
    }
    return 0;
}
